spine = read.csv("Spine.csv", header = T)
chest = read.csv("Chest.csv", header = T)
chest = chest[,2:114]
spine = spine[,2:116]
chest$PatientAge = round(chest$PatientAge/12,1)
spine$PatientAge = round(spine$PatientAge/12,1)
chest$PatientGender = factor(chest$PatientGender, levels = c(1,2), labels = c("Male", "Female"))
spine$PatientGender = factor(spine$PatientGender, levels = c(1,2), labels = c("Male", "Female"))
chest$PatientRace = factor(chest$PatientRace, levels = c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7), 
                           labels = c("White","Black", "Asian", "Hispanic", "Pacific Islander",
                                      "Mixed","Unkown"))
spine$PatientRace = factor(spine$PatientRace, levels = c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7), 
                           labels = c("White","Black", "Asian", "Hispanic", "Pacific Islander", "Mixed",
                                      "Unkown"))
par(mfrow=c(1,2))
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data = chest) + aes(x = PatientGender) + geom_bar() + 
  labs(x = "Gender", y = "Number of Patients", 
       title = "Gender Distribution of Chest Surgery Patients")

hist(chest$PatientAge, col = "lightblue", xlab = "Age", ylab = "Number of Patients", 
     main = "Chest Surgery Patients Age")
hist(chest$PatientWeight, col = "lightblue", xlab = "Weight", ylab = "Number of Patients",
     main = "Chest Surgery Patients Weight")

ggplot(data = chest) + geom_bar(aes(x = factor(1), fill = chest$PatientRace)) + 
  coord_polar(theta = "y") + ggtitle("Number of Patients of Each Race") +
  labs(x = "", y = "") 

ggplot(data = spine) + aes(x = PatientGender) + geom_bar() + 
  labs(x = "Gender", y = "Number of Patients", 
       title = "Gender Distribution of Spine Surgery Patients")

hist(spine$PatientAge, col = "lightblue", xlab = "Age", ylab = "Number of Patients", 
     main = "Spine Surgery Patient Age")
hist(spine$PatientWeight, col = "lightblue", xlab = "Weight", ylab = "Number of Patients",
     main = "Spine Surgery Patients Weight")

ggplot(data = spine) + geom_bar(aes(x = factor(1), fill = spine$PatientRace)) + 
  coord_polar(theta = "y") + ggtitle("Number of Patients of Each Race") +
  labs(x = "", y = "")

hist(chest\(PatientAge, col = "grey") hist(chest\)PatientWeight, col = “grey”) ```
